				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Tadpoling Centre (ReCon command \"oe tc_teleport\")\r\n- Interact with the mind flayer device that controls the pod.\r\n- Select the \"Release\" option.\r\n- killcombat\r\n- The Flaming Fist Manip will make this comment after some time during her idle behaviour."
